algorithm_technique: Simulates lexicographical traversal by prioritizing smaller numbers and then appending zeros.
problem_summary_simple: Return numbers from 1 to n in lexicographical order.
problem_summary_technical: Generates numbers by following a path similar to a pre-order traversal of a conceptual tree.
key_insights: The problem can be viewed as traversing a conceptual tree where nodes are numbers.
The traversal order is similar to a pre-order traversal, prioritizing smaller prefixes.
The O(1) space constraint suggests an iterative approach that directly generates the next number.
